precis:
Regulations Amending the FOOD AND DRUG REGULATIONS (1143 - CYFLUTHRIN)
which establish maximum limits (MRLs) on residues of the insecticide
cyfluthrin that can be detected in or on eggs, milk and the fat in whole
milk, and in the meat, fat and by-products of cattle, goats, hogs, horses,
poultry and sheep.
